                        └── • scan buffer
                              label: buffer 1

statement ok
INSERT INTO regional_by_row_table_virt_partial (pk, a, b) VALUES (1, 1, 1)

statement error pq: duplicate key value violates unique constraint "v_a_gt_0"\nDETAIL: Key \(v\)=\(2\) already exists\.
